{"tid":2008384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大內宣：一人藍．搵工難","createTime":"2020-05-09T04:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T11:07:04.000Z","uid":21678,"like":107,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"991ec570b37b677a7a1b5c6f85e88958a7d39b42","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:06:59.000Z","msg":"眾所周知<br />\n大多數藍絲利己主義<br />\n見錢就會跪<br />\n<br />\n要減低佢哋支持政府嘅強度<br />\n就要營造出「愈藍愈窮」嘅感覺<br />\n甚至係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「人一藍，搵工難」</span></span></strong><br />\n呢個大眾共識<br />\n<br />\n概念上即係將藍嘅深淺程度<br />\n同收入反向掛鉤<br />\n<br />\n響嚟緊幾年經濟下行嘅時候<br />\n呢個想法就會一步一步侵蝕佢哋嘅愛國心"},{"pid":"7f4b1952c8ffa2506c21d2a45fa14884e46f55e3","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"要響藍絲群組栽種呢個共識<br />\n首先須要一間「獨立民調」<br />\n例如某大學嘅抽樣電話訪問<br />\n<br />\n如果數據證明<br />\n藍絲嘅失業率遠高於黃絲<br />\n咁佢哋互相訴苦、推卸失業責任嘅時候<br />\n就自然會將呢個講法<br />\n不知不覺響peer group流傳"},{"pid":"052494f6c98c43e54b24fbc83f5b2a048f25818e","tid":2008384,"uid":100143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"791d99338a8f87afb5359e5096c2b7e2d4926724","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"親中媒體用咗幾個月時間一直抺黑黃圈<br />\n當「人一藍，搵工難」呢個講法出現嘅時候<br />\n只會順水推舟<br />\n加倍攻擊黃圈挑起矛盾<br />\n<br />\n問題係<br />\n加強卸責畀黃圈<br />\n等同於變相鞏固藍絲對<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「黃圈可以操縱藍絲生殺大權」</span></strong>呢個想法"},{"pid":"4a68f39c6831a0f91288cca6162e2ef42101dceb","tid":2008384,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8b0d0d3258e85a6222851d1e369386c9767a09b7","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"呢個思想<br />\n進一步會同藍絲祖國強大、中共超級無敵勁、藍絲實贏之類嘅信仰衝突<br />\n而產生<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「中共強大，但係冇救過我」</span></span></strong>嘅想法<br />\n繼而hang 機"},{"pid":"2ad56a03fbf8b8a98e12b48b223aaae8a9fed5ac","tid":2008384,"uid":305553,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:10:11.000Z","msg":"點解藍絲失業率一定高啲"},{"pid":"1d6d6a38f49e4f0917563a85ae1ce0edd30b3baf","tid":2008384,"uid":62318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"營造出個感覺，但現實完全相反，咁有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬都想營造佢地係正義，咁你覺得成唔成功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7117eed72e2cca7d6aa35491af48744b2fad0b97","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"既然呢個金句可以鼓勵藍絲分裂<br />\n第一步<br />\n就係搵合適嘅機構出手<br />\n<br />\n呢啲機構一定唔可以有明確嘅政治背景<br />\n但反正年紀大嘅一群，普遍偏藍<br />\n而佢哋又係零售飲食服務業嘅中流砥柱<br />\n受疫情嘅影響<br />\n本身就較高<br />\n<br />\n所以即使係中立機構<br />\n都一定會得出「人一藍，搵工難」呢個結論"},{"pid":"3a9c53d9157b2548c8d9ca9b4ca2d7c9a3476e21","tid":2008384,"uid":321374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"一隻19糉，一個發霉月餅就可以收買到既人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345e978210c4fa06428a67b7509093358424950a","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6d6a38f49e4f0917563a85ae1ce0edd30b3baf","tid":2008384,"uid":62318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"營造出個感覺，但現實完全相反，咁有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬都想營造佢地係正義，咁你覺得成唔成功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"廢老同年輕一輩嘅批判能力<br />\n點能夠相提並論？<br />\n<br />\n好多藍絲都有被害妄想症<br />\n有人一講佢哋個群組搵工難啲<br />\n佢哋實認都認唔切"},{"pid":"eab239080b7f23c76e06476bfcbffb9864bd079d","tid":2008384,"uid":171332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1eb15ed49351ad5ef373244e64ab3121f18a087","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e14dd3a8bd71aa4c89da043641d247815e74aa0","tid":2008384,"uid":108006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲會扮晒受害者，話人歧視佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住又話就業巿場不應分顏色"},{"pid":"2da31e870b2e136e054b90c09ba73586737d9f20","tid":2008384,"uid":62318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345e978210c4fa06428a67b7509093358424950a","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d6d6a38f49e4f0917563a85ae1ce0edd30b3baf","tid":2008384,"uid":62318,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"營造出個感覺，但現實完全相反，咁有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬都想營造佢地係正義，咁你覺得成唔成功？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"廢老同年輕一輩嘅批判能力<br />\n點能夠相提並論？<br />\n<br />\n好多藍絲都有被害妄想症<br />\n有人一講佢哋個群組搵工難啲<br />\n佢哋實認都認唔切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"以前我都覺得廢老同年輕人既批判能力有分別，不過最近已經開始覺得，其實一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運作既方程，其實冇分別，只不過老一輩既人要代入既數可能比較簡單，而年輕既人比較覆雜，但運算模式係同一個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得批判能力係取決於個人，而唔關年齡層事"},{"pid":"fdc1f6a280d92b24367d6a643f39709000abbbc6","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e14dd3a8bd71aa4c89da043641d247815e74aa0","tid":2008384,"uid":108006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"藍絲會扮晒受害者，話人歧視佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住又話就業巿場不應分顏色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"我就覺得應該借力打力<br />\n多啲將佢哋「不獲聘用係因為藍色政見」呢個想法<br />\n加大一千倍宣傳開去<br />\n<br />\n當佢哋面臨愈大嘅經濟壓力<br />\n愛支思想就愈受衝擊<br />\n<br />\n而家係歧視你藍色<br />\n點丫？<br />\n成條街得返黃店有生意<br />\n咁你想轉色過嚟逗返份人工<br />\n定保持深藍，等社署份老綜囉"},{"pid":"0d1a711cc81e8a58145200807fdba4786d783449","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52087af5ecd209d1815511e4406974fe21b15cf1","tid":2008384,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce565ff6436c18b03aab046cfdb7df983e009fef","tid":2008384,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"藍絲做錯野唔會認，好撚鳩麻煩"},{"pid":"cf42733ef3c28813f61283ed6ee5d02dc5a5577c","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"好多廢老仍然抱持着「只要搞事就有美國資助」呢個低能想法<br />\n其實唔應該反駁<br />\n而係有得佢哋講<br />\n<br />\n再配合藍絲會失業呢個想法<br />\n就會引發佢哋自己對自己陣營金主嘅不滿"},{"pid":"4918fcbf7e5dbe836dbf30a7958feb585a368d46","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f4ac1f7a60dcce966cb1d4788d90a0d858ebe2","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8687add7edb7592260a15e78e5bf75e62a8701","tid":2008384,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"「人一藍，搵工難」"},{"pid":"5c6a102ada80d24c987879fa11cea77d14abbac3","tid":2008384,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"有搵工呢個需要通常都後生仔 而呢班人黃一定係大多數<br />\n廢老無啦啦搵乜鳩工 本身都有職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96022f4093f8753312436c6b01326dccce89cb99","tid":2008384,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6a102ada80d24c987879fa11cea77d14abbac3","tid":2008384,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"有搵工呢個需要通常都後生仔 而呢班人黃一定係大多數<br />\n廢老無啦啦搵乜鳩工 本身都有職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月執咗幾多餐廳食肆<br />\n大量阿叔阿姐失業喎"}]}